{"tid":2240942,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《錦瑟》李商隱","createTime":"2020-10-13T04:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:12:36.000Z","uid":256952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93b297e8a4bf33ba5617933af71c0a93dde1a713","tid":2240942,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"錦瑟無端五十弦，一弦一柱思華年。<br />\n莊生曉夢迷蝴蝶，望帝春心託杜鵑。<br />\n滄海月明珠有淚，藍田日暖玉生煙。<br />\n此情可待成追憶？只是當時已惘然。"},{"pid":"9747d6704ff2406fb24a67b2eba6fdb4da236a56","tid":2240942,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96dfcd21ece6e15b83ab78ee882009caff64cbdb","tid":2240942,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"夕陽度西嶺，群壑倏已暝。<br />\n<br />\n松月生夜涼，風泉滿清聽。<br />\n<br />\n樵人歸欲盡，煙鳥棲初定。<br />\n<br />\n之子期宿來，孤琴候蘿徑。"},{"pid":"b6b6f1ef023d23465138b4eaadccb138828fc746","tid":2240942,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96dfcd21ece6e15b83ab78ee882009caff64cbdb","tid":2240942,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"夕陽度西嶺，群壑倏已暝。<br />\n<br />\n松月生夜涼，風泉滿清聽。<br />\n<br />\n樵人歸欲盡，煙鳥棲初定。<br />\n<br />\n之子期宿來，孤琴候蘿徑。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"丁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24a3f7a525f7fc40ae2bd8ebb9fae9baf6269cd","tid":2240942,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"譯文<br />\n錦瑟呀，你爲何竟有五十條弦？每弦每節，都令人懷思黃金華年。我心如莊子，爲蝴蝶曉夢而迷惘；又如望帝化杜鵑，寄託春心哀怨。滄海明月高照，鮫人泣淚皆成珠。藍田紅日和暖，可看到良玉生煙。悲歡離合之情，豈待今日來追憶，只是當年卻漫不經心，早已惘然。"},{"pid":"af34a6dc92d4cc634d3fe7bff00b3200a03bbf09","tid":2240942,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"我細個諗<br />\n<br />\n如果個時有ukulele會點"},{"pid":"58947f1b1b12c68b031742ca2bd549cbcc5480e1","tid":2240942,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af34a6dc92d4cc634d3fe7bff00b3200a03bbf09","tid":2240942,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"我細個諗<br />\n<br />\n如果個時有ukulele會點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"三味線<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173028ceb69b11dd45317d9ef42b449f7bacf5dc","tid":2240942,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4158720f862e9750922020af38e4b30ffa6273db","tid":2240942,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"天空有些暗了，暗的剛剛好。<br />\n我難過的樣子就沒人看到。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501dd203c4222a3bbedcbd41574958cf5ea56514","tid":2240942,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173028ceb69b11dd45317d9ef42b449f7bacf5dc","tid":2240942,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"🍷🍷🍷🍷🍷🍷"},{"pid":"4d719e37364369bd459eddc75